हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
In a remote tech facility, captives are stripped of their memories and identities—engineered into something new. Among them, one woman begins to remember: her true self and the sister she lost.
A tense fight for freedom, family, and identity unfolds—where betrayal, fear, and control must be confronted head-on.
